1. *Boj* je počeo u zoru. (The battle began at dawn.)
2. Učestvovao sam u *boju*. (I participated in the battle.)
3. Ratni *bojevi* su bili teški. (The battles of war were tough.)
4. Na zastavi su bili *bojevi* Srbije. (The colors of Serbia were on the flag.)
5. *Boje* su mi omiljene. (Colors are my favorite.)
6. Moramo *bojiti* ovaj zid. (We need to paint this wall.)
7. Kupio sam novi *bojler*. (I bought a new water heater.)
8. *Boja* kose joj se dopada. (She likes the color of her hair.)
9. Koliko *boja* postoji u spektru? (How many colors are there in the spectrum?)
10. Imam *bojazan* da se nećemo uspeti izboriti. (I'm afraid we won't succeed.)

Note: The word "boj" has multiple meanings in Serbian, such as "battle," "color," "paint," "water heater," "fear," etc.